---
title: Lamb Shortloin & Dukkah Roasted Veggies with Jewelled Israeli Couscous & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Sear a tender and succulent lamb loin that's just right for a gourmet-style dinner. With all the flavour of traditional roast lamb, plus wholesome veggies with a hit of toasted dukkah, it's sure to have you feeling satisfied with every delicious mouthful.
